con:eventHandlers.name: RequestFilter.filterRequest
con:eventHandlers.con:script:
import com.eviware.soapui.support.XmlHolder
def holder = new XmlHolder(context.requestContent) holder.namespaces["wsa"] = "http://www.w3.org/2005/08/addressing" holder.namespaces["s"] = "http://schemas.xmlsoap.org/soap/envelope/" holder.namespaces["hl7"] = "urn:hl7-org:v3"
def messageIdNode = holder.getDomNode("//wsa:MessageID") def messageId = messageIdNode.valueAsString def idNode = holder.getDomNode("//s:Body/*[1]/hl7:id") if (!idNode) return messageId = messageId.replaceAll('uuid:', '') messageIdNode.firstChild.nodeValue = messageId
idNode.getAttributeNode('root').setValue(messageId) context.requestContent = holder.xml
